cast.overview: The crew of a horror web series travels to an abandoned asylum for a live broadcast, but they encounter much more than expected as they move deeper inside the nightmarish old building.
cast.title: Gonjiam: Haunted Asylum

details.biography: Joo Ye-bin (주예빈) is a South Korean host and actress. Originally devoted herself to the theater world, she has now retired from the adult film industry and returned to full-time career as a theater actress, and has experience working as a photo model while working under the name of Jo Ji-yeong (2013-2017). Before becoming active in the theater world, she takes good care of her body due to her experience as a belly dancer. She is also the recipient of the 2020 Korean Theater Actors Association Newcomer of the Year Award.
details.name: Joo Ye-bin
